------------------------------------POST----------------------------------------------
1. Add User : Method "POST"
2. URL: http://localhost:9092/loginController/addUser
3. INPUT: 
   Body -> Raw -> JSON
   {
   "adminId" : 101,
   "adminUsername" : "ram",
   "adminPassword" : "ram@123"
	}
	
------------------------------------GET----------------------------------------------
1. Get User : Method "GET"
2. URL:	http://localhost:9092/loginController/viewAllUsers

------------------------------------DELETE----------------------------------------------
1. Delete User : Method "DELETE"
2. URL: http://localhost:9092/loginController/removeUser
3. INPUT: 
   Body -> Raw -> JSON  
	{
   "adminId" : 106,
   "adminUsername" : "Nikhil",
   "adminPassword" : "Nikhil@123"
	}